cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper involves the use of deep learning for image-based tracking and volume reconstruction, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The simultaneous localisation and mapping (SLAM) algorithm used in the paper is a common technique in robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves the use of weak annotation, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of ultrasound images, which falls under graphics (cs.GR).
